==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Feller
<hw>Fell"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who, or that
which, fells, knocks or cuts down; a machine for felling
trees.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Feller</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Feller
<hw>Fell"er</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An appliance to a sewing machine
for felling a seam.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fellfare</ent>⟦br⟧
